GK19jalmugiu:209: vaidhavyaṃ na ca bādhate sadasatoḥ saṃbḥāvanā vyatyayāt JMu_53b
GK19jalmugiu:210: vaiyarthyaṃ navayauvanasya kim api premṇaḥ kalaṅkāṅkuraḥ JMu_24b
GK19jalmugiu:211: vyākhyātaṃ guṇadoṣajātam ucitaṃ cintyaṃ tad apy ādarāt JMu_54d
GK19jalmugiu:213: vyājānāṃ prathamāya garbhagaṇikārāgāya tubhyaṃ namaḥ JMu_2d
GK19jalmugiu:214: vyādhir nādhir asatsutapratinidhis trāso na bhṛtyoḥ samaḥ JMu_20b
GK19jalmugiu:215: śākhī rāhur api grahaḥ sa ca bhaved uṣṭro 'pi kiṃ vā[ha]tam JMu_21b
GK19jalmugiu:216: śāpaḥ ko 'pi mahānayaṃ pariṇatir duṣkarmaṇām īdṛśī JMu_26a
GK19jalmugiu:218: śuddho vipra ivāntyajaṃ janapadaḥ śrīmān iva śvitriṇam JMu_13b
GK19jalmugiu:220: śūlenādya mṛtāham adya sarajāḥ kartavyam adya vrataṃ JMu_35a
GK19jalmugiu:221: śṛṅgārasya viḍambanā kim aparaṃ veśyārataḍambaraḥ JMu_24d
GK19jalmugiu:224: śrīputrais taruṇais tathā navanavair vārāṅganā krīḍati JMu_15d
GK19jalmugiu:225: śrīmantaṃ śirasā bibharti kurute viśvabhramaṃ helayā JMu_4a
GK19jalmugiu:227: ślāghārho vyasanīti hīnakula ity agryaḥ kuṭumbaḥ svayam JMu_31b
GK19jalmugiu:228: śvaityaṃ kalpaya kajjale kapikuleṣv āropayācāpalaṃ JMu_6a
GK19jalmugiu:229: saṅgītaṃ rajanī vidhur madhumadaḥ spardhā sapatnais tathā JMu_43c
GK19jalmugiu:231: saptāṅgavyasanāvaleḥ praśamanopāyaś ca śikṣā satām JMu_61d
GK19jalmugiu:232: sarvasya vyasanaṃ kilaitad adhikaṃ tatrāpi veśyeti ca JMu_54b
GK19jalmugiu:233: sarvasvakṣapaṇāya kevalam aho mūrkhāḥ sukhenāsate JMu_5d
GK19jalmugiu:235: sarvāvastha iti pramāṇapuruṣo veśyābhir abhyarcyate JMu_31d
GK19jalmugiu:236: saśrīkaḥ kamalākaraś ca suṣamāṃ kāṃ kām aho nārhati JMu_60d
GK19jalmugiu:238: saṃbhūyāpi ca yat surāsurabalair unmathya pāthonidher JMu_11c
GK19jalmugiu:239: saṃsārasya maheśvaro dinapatir dhvāntasya vaidyo rujāṃ JMu_61a
GK19jalmugiu:240: saḥ kruddho gamitas tvayeti kalaho mātrā samaṃ jāyate JMu_49b
GK19jalmugiu:241: sā kiṃ śrīr upabhogam arhati na yā sevyaḥ sa kiṃ yo 'ntaraṃ JMu_22c
GK19jalmugiu:242: sāndrānandakarambitaṃ jagad idaṃ vindanti nindanti ca JMu_64d
GK19jalmugiu:245: sītkārāntarasatyam arthaharaṇaṃ sarvatra ye jānate JMu_41c
GK19jalmugiu:246: sopekṣair iva cakṣuṣoḥ saralitāpāṅgaiś ca bhaṅgyantaraiḥ JMu_47b
GK19jalmugiu:247: so 'yaṃ saṃprati Jalhaṇena kavinā Mudghopadeśaḥ kṛtaḥ JMu_65d
GK19jalmugiu:248: saujanyena gataṃ kim anyad aphalo rāśir guṇānām api JMu_44b
GK19jalmugiu:249: saundaryasya samunnates taralatā jñānasya garvagrahaḥ JMu_18b
GK19jalmugiu:252: sauhārdasya ca vibhramasya ca rater bhartuś ca yūnāṃ tathā JMu_26c
GK19jalmugiu:254: strīti prītikaraṃ puraḥ pariṇatau hālāhalaṃ kevalaṃ JMu_54a
GK19jalmugiu:255: snehānāṃ kaṇikāpi nāsti gaṇikālokasya ca prāyaśaḥ JMu_9d
GK19jalmugiu:257: svapne kām api saṃsmaran priya mayā dṛṣṭo 'si tat te balād JMu_46a
GK19jalmugiu:258: svasbhānur vidhumaṇḍalasya vaḍavāvakro nidher ambhasā JMu_17c
GK19jalmugiu:259: svādhīno bhṛtako jaḍo guṇarataś cauro vyapetaspṛhaḥ JMu_8b
GK19jalmugiu:260: svāmī krūram ivāśritaṃ pariṇato yogīva saṃsāriṇaṃ JMu_13a
GK19jalmugiu:263: hevākena kavir madena kulajaḥ krodhāgninā tāpasaḥ JMu_16b
